OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782497915
OL,3,CLabour politicians urge rethink on
OL,4,Cscrapped plans to dual A1 in
OL,5,CNorthumberland
OL,7,FLabour politicians in Northumberland
OL,8,Fhave called on the Chancellor to
OL,9,Frevisit her decision to scrap plans to
OL,10,Fdual a section of the A1 in
OL,11,FNorthumberland.
OL,13,FIn an open letter to Rachel Reeves,
OL,14,FNorth Northumberland MP David Smith,
OL,15,FHexham MP Joe Morris, North-East Mayor
OL,16,FKim McGuinness and Northumberland
OL,17,FCounty Council Labour Group Leader
OL,18,FScott Dickinson have urged the
OL,19,FTreasury to provide "heavyweight
OL,20,Finvestment" to the scheme.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
