OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782497915
OL,3,CLabour politicians urge rethink on
OL,4,Cscrapped plans to dual A1 in
OL,5,CNorthumberland
OL,7,FPreviously approved plans to dual the
OL,8,Froad were scrapped in the 2024 budget,
OL,9,Fwith the Chancellor calling the plans
OL,10,F"unfunded and unaffordable".
OL,12,FHowever, the government has faced
OL,13,Fsustained pressure to revisit the
OL,14,Fdecision from local leaders from both
OL,15,FLabour and the Conservatives, with
OL,16,Feight people having died in accidents
OL,17,Fon the road so far this year.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
