OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782497915
OL,3,CLabour politicians urge rethink on
OL,4,Cscrapped plans to dual A1 in
OL,5,CNorthumberland
OL,7,FThe open letter reads: "The scheme has
OL,8,Fthe potential to strengthen
OL,9,Fconnectivity, drive economic growth,
OL,10,Fimprove network resilience, and unlock
OL,11,Fsignificant opportunities across the
OL,12,FNorth East.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782497915
OL,3,CLabour politicians urge rethink on
OL,4,Cscrapped plans to dual A1 in
OL,5,CNorthumberland
OL,7,F"The dualling of the 50 miles of A1
OL,8,Fbetween Morpeth and Berwick is a
OL,9,Ftotemic issue for Northumberland and
OL,10,Fincreasingly for the wider North East.
OL,11,FIt is an issue decades in the making,
OL,12,Fwhich successive governments - most
OL,13,Frecently the 2010-2024 Conservative
OL,14,FGovernment - have failed to
OL,15,Fsubstantially address.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782497915
OL,3,CLabour politicians urge rethink on
OL,4,Cscrapped plans to dual A1 in
OL,5,CNorthumberland
OL,7,F"If this Labour Government that is
OL,8,Fdoing so much investment into public
OL,9,Finfrastructure could make progress on
OL,10,Fthe A1 we could save countless lives,
OL,11,Frestore confidence and cement our role
OL,12,Fas the champion of our Northern
OL,13,Fcommunities."
OL,15,FThe letter calls for a clear timeline
OL,16,Fand funding commitment to get "spades
OL,17,Fin the ground" for the work before the
OL,18,Fnext general election, as well as a
OL,19,Fbroader strategy to address "historic
OL,20,Funderfunding of rural transport
OL,21,Finfrastructure"
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782497915
OL,3,CLabour politicians urge rethink on
OL,4,Cscrapped plans to dual A1 in
OL,5,CNorthumberland
OL,7,FNorth Northumberland MP David Smith
OL,8,Fsaid: "The A1 is not safe enough. I
OL,9,Fhave always wanted dualling in the
OL,10,Flong-term and my short-term focus has
OL,11,Fbeen on securing sensible safety
OL,12,Fimprovements from Morpeth to Berwick.
OL,13,FWe need and deserve both.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782497915
OL,3,CLabour politicians urge rethink on
OL,4,Cscrapped plans to dual A1 in
OL,5,CNorthumberland
OL,7,F"Now we've got some initial
OL,8,Fimprovements secured we can turn our
OL,9,Fattention to getting the much larger
OL,10,Finvestment the road ultimately needs.
OL,11,FI want dualling to be part of the
OL,12,Fconversation for the sake and safety
OL,13,Fof my constituents and all who use
OL,14,Fthis major road.
OL,16,F"Finally, I would like to send my
OL,17,Fheartfelt thanks to our emergency
OL,18,Fservices, for their unwavering skills
OL,19,Fand expertise in handling so many
OL,20,Ftragedies this year. They are the
OL,21,Funsung heroes of this moment."
OL,26,@}D@^O]
